message: "If you use Promptise Foundry in academic work or production systems, please cite it."
title: "Promptise Foundry: The foundation layer for agentic intelligence"
abstract: >-
  Promptise Foundry is one framework to go from prototype to production.
  Agents that discover tools, remember context, and guard themselves.
  MCP servers with auth, governance, and audit trails. A Reasoning
  Engine to build how your agent thinks — like bricks. Deploy
  autonomous agents that work around the clock — with lifecycle
  management, crash recovery, and mission-driven execution.
